    "description_long": "This is a portable road work detour ahead sign featuring a bright orange diamond-shaped panel with a black pictogram of a construction worker using a shovel. The sign is mounted on a sturdy metal tripod stand with four legs, each tipped with orange for visibility. Two orange square flags are attached to the top of the sign, enhancing its visibility to oncoming traffic. The reverse side of the sign is plain, showing the metallic backing and support structure. The overall construction appears lightweight yet stable, designed for quick deployment and removal in urban or roadside environments.",
